These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-1::.
There 4 different types of food: potato, cauliflower, pomegranate, radish
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, lizard, mouse, rat
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: horror, spy, sports, documentary
1. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
2. the person eating pomegranate is on the left of the person eating potato##1
3. the person eating radish is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
4. the person eating potato is the owner of the chinchilla##1
5. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
6. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
7. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Food    | cauliflower  | radish | pomegranate    | potato       |
| Pet         | lizard | rat    | mouse      | chinchilla |
| Movie-Genre   | horror   | sports | spy | documentary        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-2::.
House: farmhouse, victorian, palace, ranch-style
The people have 4 different jobs:  fisherman, lawyer, musician, social-worker
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, may, august, september
1. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the social-worker##1
2. the ranch-style house is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
3. the musician is on the right of the palace house##1
4. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
5. the person who's birthday is in july is the fisherman##1
6. the person who's birthday is in september is the victorian house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2     |       3       |     4     |
| House        | palace   | victorian | farmhouse     | ranch-style      |
| Job         | lawyer | musician | social-worker | fisherman |
| Birthday   | may    | september   | august     | july      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-3::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, satire, mystery, western
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, electronic, hip-hop, pop
4 different pets are kept: bird, goldfish, turtle, hamster
1. the fan of electronic is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1
2. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
3. the fan of pop is on the far left##1
4. the person watching western movies is the fan of hip-hop##1
5. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
6. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
7. the person watching animation movies is the owner of the bird##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |    3    |      4      |
| Movie-Genre         | animation | satire | mystery | western |
| Music-Genre   | pop       | electronic    | country | hip-hop     |
| Pet   | bird | turtle    | hamster | goldfish    |

