.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-4::.
4 different games are played: canasta, chess, whist, mah-jongg
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rowing, rugby, soccer, volleyball
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, may, october, march
1. the person playing whist is the person who's birthday is in march##1
2. the person who's sport is rugby is on the far left##1
3. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
4. the person playing chess is on the far right##1
5. the person who's sport is soccer is on the far right##1
6. the person who's sport is rowing is the person playing whist##1
7. the person playing whist is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
8. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |        2        |     3      |      4      |
| Game         | canasta | mah-jongg | whist | chess |
| Sport       | rugby     | volleyball      | rowing     | soccer      |
| Birthday   | may | november         | march      | october        |

