.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-5::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, drawing, singing, video-games
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, cola, sprite, iced-tea
There are 4 different favourite colors: ivory, emerald, brown, green
1. the person drinking cola is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is singing is on the far left##1
3. the person who likes emerald is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
4. the person who likes ivory is the person drinking sprite##1
5. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person who likes emerald##1
6. the person who's hobby is cooking is the person drinking cola##1
7. the person who's hobby is video-games is the person who likes brown##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3     |      4       |
| Hobby         | singing   | video-games | drawing  | cooking      |
| Beverage   | sprite  | milk        | iced-tea  | cola       |
| Color         | ivory | brown    | emerald | green |

