.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-6::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, train, boat, taxi
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, horror, mystery, satire
4 different pets are kept: cat, ferret, hamster, hedgehog
1. the person driving the helicopter is the owner of the ferret##1
2. the owner of the cat is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
3. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
4. the owner of the hedgehog is on the far left##1
5. the person driving the train is on the far left##1
6. the person watching mystery movies is the person driving the boat##1
7. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
8. the person driving the taxi is the owner of the hamster##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3    |     4      |
| Transport           | train | boat | taxi | helicopter |
| Movie-Genre   | satire   | mystery  | horror | disaster   |
| Pet   | hedgehog   | cat     | hamster | ferret       |

