.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-7::.
House: colonial, townhouse, victorian, ranch-style
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, cooking, skydiving, video-games
There are 4 different favourite colors: aquamarine, lavender, purple, emerald
1. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the far right##1
2. the townhouse house is on the far right##1
3. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left of the person who likes lavender##1
4. the person who likes lavender is the victorian house##1
5. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the colonial house##1
6. the person who likes purple is on the left of the person who likes aquamarine##1
7. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
8. the person who's hobby is cooking is the person who likes aquamarine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |    3    |     4     |
| House          | colonial  | ranch-style | victorian   | townhouse     |
| Hobby         | video-games | cooking   | baking  | skydiving |
| Color   | purple         | aquamarine  | lavender | emerald  |

