.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-8::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, iced-tea, juice, soy-milk
There 4 different types of food: pepper, garlic, mango, strawberry
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: r&b, gospel, disco, funk
1. the person drinking iced-tea is the fan of disco##1
2. the fan of funk is on the right of the person eating strawberry##1
3. the person eating garlic is on the far right##1
4. the person eating mango is on the left of the fan of disco##1
5. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person eating pepper##1
6. the fan of funk is the person drinking juice##1
7. the fan of gospel is on the left of the fan of funk##1
8. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | soy-milk | juice     | almond-milk | iced-tea |
| Food   | strawberry  | pepper | mango       | garlic    |
| Music-Genre   | gospel   | funk | r&b    | disco |

