.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-9::.
City: edinburgh, liverpool, san-francisco, boston
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, oliveros, davidoff, baccarat
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, skateboarding, soccer, water-polo
1. the oliveros-smoker is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1
2. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
3. the oliveros-smoker is on the left of the davidoff-smoker##1
4. the person who's sport is soccer is the person traveling to liverpool##1
5. the person traveling to liverpool is on the right of the baccarat-smoker##1
6. the baccarat-smoker is on the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
7. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |   3    |     4      |
| City          | san-francisco        | boston   | liverpool  | edinburgh   |
| Cigar   | old-henry         | baccarat     | oliveros    | davidoff       |
| Sport         | skateboarding | lacrosse | soccer | water-polo |

