There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, australian, russian, french
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, mouse, rabbit, turtle
1. the person who's sport is soccer is the owner of the turtle##1
2. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
3. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the australian##1
4. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
5. the russian is on the far right##1
6. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
7. the argentine is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Sport   | handball    | badminton | soccer | climbing        |
| Nationality       | french | argentine  | australian | russian     |
| Pet        | mouse    | rabbit   | turtle  | chinchilla |

