.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-11::.
City: edinburgh, miami, venice, san-francisco
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, rugby, volleyball, weightlifting
House: wooden, victorian, townhouse, modern
1. the wooden house is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the person traveling to miami##1
3. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
4. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
5. the modern house is on the right of the victorian house##1
6. the wooden house is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
7. the person who's sport is cricket is the townhouse house##1
8. the person who's sport is volleyball is the person traveling to edinburgh##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |      2       |       3       |       4       |
| City         | edinburgh  | san-francisco | miami  | venice |
| Sport       | volleyball | rugby        | weightlifting | cricket       |
| House   | wooden   | victorian          | modern          | townhouse       |

