1. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the prince-smoker##1
2. the cain-smoker is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
3. the person who growslily is on the left of the person who growsrose##1
4. the cain-smoker is on the right of the old-henry-smoker##1
5. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
6. the person who's hobby is card-games is the person who growszinnia##1
7. the person who growslily is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby         | traveling   | dancing   | card-games | cooking |
| Cigar   | dunhill | prince | old-henry   | cain |
| Flower   | lily     | rose  | zinnia  | sunflower  |

