3. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1
4. the person traveling to colone is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
5. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person traveling to berlin##1
6. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person watching comedy movies##1
7. the person watching mystery movies is on the far right##1
8. the person playing go is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |     3     |     4      |
