.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-15::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, february, november, may
There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, dutch, french, colombian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, handball, soccer, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is climbing is the person who's birthday is in november##1
2. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the dutch##1
3. the dutch is on the right of the colombian##1
4. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
5. the colombian is the person who's birthday is in may##1
6. the french is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
7. the person who's birthday is in september is the chinese##1
8. the french is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |    3     |    4     |
| Birthday      | september        | may    | february | november      |
| Nationality   | chinese        | colombian   | dutch  | french  |
| Sport         | weightlifting | handball | soccer   | climbing |

