3. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
4. the person playing domino is the person who's sport is basketball##1
5. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
6. the person watching superhero movies is the person playing snooker##1
7. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3     |     4     |
