4. the person eating kiwi is on the left of the person who likes emerald##1
5. the person eating kale is on the far right##1
6. the person who likes emerald is on the left of the person who likes purple##1
7. the mexican is on the left of the person who likes yellow##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |    3    |    4    |
| Nationality   | british | indonesian | mexican | russian |
