.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-20::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: zinnia, tulip, sunflower, balloon-flower
There are 4 different nationalities: indonesian, nigerian, pakistani, russian
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: sports, martial-arts, thriller, satire
1. the person who growstulip is on the left of the indonesian##1
2. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the person who growssunflower##1
3. the person watching satire movies is on the far right##1
4. the pakistani is on the far right##1
5. the indonesian is the person watching thriller movies##1
6. the russian is on the far left##1
7. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the far right##1
8. the russian is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |       4        |
| Flower           | tulip  | sunflower  | zinnia | balloon-flower |
| Nationality   | russian   | indonesian | nigerian   | pakistani      |
| Movie-Genre         | sports | thriller    | martial-arts   | satire         |

 